      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "- Landing & Takeoff movements\n- Unconstrained & constrained causing disruptions\n- Simple capacity model: 7 movements per 10 minutes\n- All runways are the same (no individual runways)\n- Fixed number for takeoff and for landing (2 + 2 by default)",
