      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "- Landing & Takeoff movements\n- Unconstrained & constrained causing disruptions\n- Simple capacity model: 7 movements per 10 minutes\n- All runways are the same (no individual runways)\n- Fixed number for takeoff and for landing (2 + 2 by default)",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
